org.apache.jena.hadoop.rdf.types

Class CharacteristicWritable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.hadoop.rdf.types.CharacteristicWritable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<CharacteristicWritable>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable, org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<CharacteristicWritable>

    public class CharacteristicWritable
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<CharacteristicWritable>
    Represents a characteristic for a single node and contains the node and a count associated with that node

    Note that characteristics are compared based upon only the nodes and not their counts
